Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎根本没办法保存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't seem to save anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是崩溃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It just keeps crashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有意思  美女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Interesting, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上一次升级系统是什么时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When was the last time you did a system upgrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为自己这是在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道规矩的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  住手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许...碰我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No... touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们玩得这些游戏...没一个起作用的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All these games we play... none of them work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  许  碰  我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You do not lay hands on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前从没这么做过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've never done this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:08:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能碰你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't touch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拥有世界上最大的IT公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I own the biggest IT company in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人人都对我有所求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone wants something from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人人都想要我给予的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone wants what I have to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我简直如同上帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's like I'm a fucking god.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我来这里  以求恢复一些平衡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I come here to restore some balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我还以为你会和其他人不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I thought that you were different than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人和我一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are no others like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很特别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上  我  确实很特别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As a matter of fact, I am special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为我选择了和你共度良宵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I choose to spend my time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我是个女神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I am a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不过是在做戏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're smoke and mirrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是个演员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you're a showgirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这是你的舞台\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this is your stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由威廉·亨廷顿·桑德斯支付购买\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}bought and paid for by William Huntington Sanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你可以喊我比尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you can call me Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全不知道我到底是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have no idea who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然知道你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know exactly who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我会展示给你看的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I will show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你想要的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this what you wanted?
