Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}机密  本人亲启
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}科里亚达节\N卓娅·维切恩亚亚家人邀请您一起追思\N我们的晚间之星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最亲爱的影子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My dearest Shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须谈谈你的头脑和内心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must speak of your head and your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}邀请您来悼念我们的晚间之星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请尽快前来  卓娅·维切恩亚亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please attend. Urgently, Zorya Polunochnaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  别忘了带上硬币\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Also, don't forget to bring the coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看在上帝的份上  迈克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For heaven's sake, Mike,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你体温过低前快上车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}get in the car before you get hypothermia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这样的天气下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In weather like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿着不合适的衣服在外面待了五分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're out there for five minutes with improper attire,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会儿你唯一能搭的车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and well, the only ride you're gonna need
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是去欧克莱尔验尸官那里的车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is to the coroner's in Eau Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正要进城买件外套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was walking into town to buy a jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好你长得帅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a good thing you're pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这辆漂亮的老古董\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah! Look at the beautiful clunker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老古董\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clunker?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年  我们找一辆报废的车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every year, we take a wreck,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它放在湖面上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we put it out on the lake,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  大家会猜测春天将至时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then, folks guess the date and the time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废车压破冰面的日期和时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when it'll break through the ice come spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  获胜者和高中平分奖金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then, the winner splits the pot with the high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会喜欢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're gonna love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}湖畔镇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然湖畔镇以渔业闻名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, while Lakeside is known for its fishing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}全美最棒的馅饼之乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但真正让我们出名的是好吃到死的馅饼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's the to-die-for pasties that put us on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}圣诞馅饼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一口都像温暖的拥抱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every delicious bite is like a warm hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你知道这地方最特别的是什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you know what really makes this place special?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:15:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的每个人都真心关心他们的邻居\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone here genuinely cares for their neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们一切行为的出发点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's in everything we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种精神是由本镇第一位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This spirit was passed down to us
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居民及资助人莱斯特·汉密尔顿传给我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by the town's first citizen and benefactor, Lester Hamilton.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他死后  将财产留给了湖畔镇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when he died, he left Lakeside his fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是镇民才能继续繁荣昌盛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that its citizens would continue to prosper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只要求我们尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All he asked in return was that we honor
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一些他最喜欢的旧世界传统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}some of his favorite Old World traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以每年我们都会举办一个冰雪节\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So every year, we hold an ice festival
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来庆祝他的慷慨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to celebrate his generosity
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢我们神奇的小镇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and give thanks for our magical little town
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及此处的北欧传统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and its Nordic heritage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你会喜欢这里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you're gonna like it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可抗力鼠脸假蝇鱼钩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rat-Faced Irresistible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦你有这些宝贝的消息传出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The trout'll jump into your frying pan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳟鱼都会自己跳进你的煎锅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}once word gets out you got one of these babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安玛莉  你要把这可怜人的耳朵都唠叨掉了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You talking this poor man's ear off, Ann-Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,李·亨宁斯  店主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lee Hennings, proprietor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克·安塞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mike Ainsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗  安塞尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What can we do for you, Mr. Ainsel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得给这家伙找件比运动衫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to get this fella into something warmer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更暖和的衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than a sweatshirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用特别硬核的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing too hardcore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道我会在这个地方待多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not sure how long I'll be in this part of the country for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是戈尔曼街的新租客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's the new tenant on Gorman Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈尔曼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gorman? Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还在想什么时候会有人搬进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were wondering when somebody was gonna move in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉森  你能带安塞尔先生去看看大衣吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alison, can you show Mr. Ainsel the parkas, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞节后  我们的毛衣也有大减价的活动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we've got some great after-Christmas sales on sweaters, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚  在巴士外面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last night, outside of the bus,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和我朋友太胡闹了  我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}um, my friend and I were being jerks. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天过得很糟糕  让我开心一下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was having a bad day. Made me smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是大衣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, well, here are the parkas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是打折的毛衣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, um, here are the on-sale sweaters,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就我来说  我会避开圣诞节款式的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}although, personally, I'd avoid the Christmas ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们超级土的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're super lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这件怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's see what this one looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:16:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说  看起来很适合你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean... I mean it seems to fit you really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对我来说就够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that is good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我买了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  来看毛衣  有驯鹿的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, these sweaters. Anything in reindeer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  有的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, yeah, yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉森  我们卖安塞尔先生一张破车票怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What say we sell Mr. Ainsel a clunker ticket, Alison?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正想问呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was just about to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需要选个日期和时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just need to, uh, pick a date and a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得它什么时候会压穿冰层\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When do you think it will go through the ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}三月  破车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3月23日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}March 23rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上七点到八点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}7 p.m. till 8 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  大多数人都会多选几天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Uh, most people pick more than one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我猜这就是你的策略吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, uh, I guess this is your strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我想我必须欣赏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Well, I guess I gotta admire
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个相信自己直觉的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a man who goes with his instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你好运  一共五美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good luck. Five dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪颗牙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which one of your teeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are loose, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这颗吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it this one here? Ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么糟糕  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now that wasn't so bad, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么糟  你猜怎么着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Hey, I'll tell you what,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能让我留下这颗臼齿做研究\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll pay you twice the Tooth Fairy's going rate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你牙仙两倍的价钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if I may keep this molar for my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}泰瑞尔合作公司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的士兵最早是什么时候带着图腾去战斗的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When did our soldiers first carry our totems into battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古德弗雷德进攻法兰克但是搞砸了那时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When Gudfred fucked up that Frankish business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上一次是约克镇战役\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The last time was Yorktown.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不再做黑森佣兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We abandoned our post as Hessian Jaegers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后加入了华盛顿的军队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and joined Washington's ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争的艺术有一半是知道何时转移阵营\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Half the art of war is knowing when to switch sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你混得挺好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have done well for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还挺舒适的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I'm comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提尔  北欧战神  舒适\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tyr, the warlord, comfortable?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,角斗士的杀戮欲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the gladiator's bloodlust
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖相不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}doesn't make for a very lucrative business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果你需要战神出场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ha! But if it's a war god you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只需要你捐个款就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I want from you is a donation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受宠若惊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}冬至暖愉\N爱你\N德墨忒尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你大老远过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You came all this way
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本来可以在芝加哥见我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when you could have put the touch on me in Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科里亚达节\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At the Koliada?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}科里亚达节\N卓娅·维切恩亚亚家人邀请您一起追思\N我们的晚间之星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芝加哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了卓娅·维切恩亚亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For Zorya Vechernyaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能等到那个时候吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Couldn't wait 'til then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起诉战争是一个费时费力的差事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prosecuting the war is an all-consuming endeavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有事情在最后一刻出现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Things come up all the time, last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然追悼会是好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Memorials are all well and good,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们都知道以牙还牙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we both know that an eye for an eye
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不便宜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}don't come cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切为了事业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, anything for the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该署名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should I make it out to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡什[现金]就好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Cash" Will be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真大方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(190,270)}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\i1\fsp1\b0\bord0\shad0\c&H7BE6FF&}我在你身边战斗  奥丁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(190,270)}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\i1\fsp1\b0\bord0\shad0\c&H7BE6FF&}战斗至死  或者杀死我们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的牙怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are your teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice try.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好啊  萨尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, top of the morning to you, Sal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.49,0:21:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我说到哪了  对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, where was I? Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湖畔新闻社就在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, Lakeside News is just down that-a-way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是扎克里·摩根在1902年创建的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was started by Zachary Morgan in 1902.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他得了梅毒  穿着尿不湿死的  可怜的家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He died of syphilis wearing a diaper, poor fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错  其实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice. Um, so actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪  但愿你是在给你老婆买礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Andy! I hope you're looking for a present for your wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个的结婚纪念日马上到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your anniversary is coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他经常忘记一些事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He happens to forget things
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像结婚纪念日这种  一年一次的婚姻事件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like annual marital events, like anniversaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅宝家餐馆就在这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mabel's Restaurant is right over here,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.06,0:22:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的馅饼  就像我之前说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the pasties, as I mentioned earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直棒极了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are the best things ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗  她传承了她奶奶的配方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, she inherited the recipe from her grandmother,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而她奶奶是从康沃尔郡带来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who brought it over here from Cornwall.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能不能快速插一句\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I could just sneak in
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问一下我在哪里能租一辆车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a quick question about where to rent a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.59,0:22:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你应该找欧克莱尔  那\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, that's Eau Claire, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从玛莎那里听说凯西的内衣被偷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard from Martha that Kathy's unmentionables were stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是直接从洗衣篮里偷的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}right from her laundry basket!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know, I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.42,0:22:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先不要因为一点点谣言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's not all get in a fuss
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就大惊小怪的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}over the Piggly Wiggly rumor mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你好啊  安玛丽  -你好  柴德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, hey, Ann-Marie. - Hi, Chad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.47,0:22:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克  看起来李·亨宁斯把你照顾得挺好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Mike. I see Lee Henning's taken good care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.22,0:22:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你看起来更像本地人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you're lookin' more local.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少暖和了不少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lot warmer at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅格·冈瑟在激动什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's Meg Gunther in a lather about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.95,0:22:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内衣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lingerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.57,0:22:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然  她的一周一轮的内衣丢了三套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apparently, three pairs of her days-of-the-week underwear:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期三的  星期四的和星期六的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wednesday, Thursday, and Saturday,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全从烘干机里消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all went missing from the dryer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她就认为  我们有一个  在逃内衣贼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, in her mind, we have a, uh, panty thief on the loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.50,0:22:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  迈克  这就算得上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See, Mike, this is what qualifies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湖畔镇的重罪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as major crime here in Lakeside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.14,0:22:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俗话说得好  如果你有钱  你在蒙特卡洛生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, if you're rich, you live in Monte Carlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你出名  就住在加州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you're famous, you live in California.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.27,0:22:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果你很幸运  那你就住在这  湖畔镇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if you're lucky, you live here in... in Lakeside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死  我要去水湾那里找巴特了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shoot. I'm supposed to meet Bart up at the inlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太抱歉了  柴德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am so sorry. Um, hey, Chad,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.83,0:23:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能不能带我们的新人去尝尝馅饼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}could you get our newest resident situated with a pasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不用再问我第二遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you don't have to ask me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我要饿死了  -太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm starving. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-来吧  -好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.38,0:23:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢你  -你肯定会喜欢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. - You're gonna love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗  有趣的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, interestingly, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.93,0:23:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅宝的美味馅饼配方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mabel's amazing pasty recipe,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.05,0:23:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实她是传承她奶奶的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she actually inherited from her grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.93,0:23:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大老远从康沃尔郡来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Came all the way from Cornwall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Grab a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.54,0:23:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好啊  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How you doing this morning, sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.81,0:23:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅宝  这是迈克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Mabel, this is Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他住在戈尔曼街\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's staying up at the spot on Gorman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.95,0:23:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你  迈克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's nice to meet you, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.51,0:23:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看看菜单吗  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I show you a menu, hon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在说馅饼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, everyone's been talking about these pasties.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.74,0:23:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一份馅饼  店里赠送\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One pasty on the house it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.51,0:23:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免费赠送给第一次光顾的顾客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's complimentary to first-time customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.99,0:23:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  能不能再来杯咖啡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you. Can I get a coffee too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经知道这牛仔要吃什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I already know what this cowboy's having.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穆里根局长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chief Mulligan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's good?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.00,0:23:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让我干等着  小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't leave me hanging, dawg.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.66,0:24:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识德瑞克吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know Derek?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.76,0:24:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不认识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.35,0:24:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他只是想让我知道有他这么个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think he just wants me to know he's down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.48,0:24:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是做什么工作的  迈克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what do you do for a living, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.79,0:24:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就替我叔叔干活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just working for my uncle right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.46,0:24:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是做什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.71,0:24:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他做进出口贸易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He runs an import-export business.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.61,0:24:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  哪一种\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah? What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.39,0:24:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分都是古董\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Antiques, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.77,0:24:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我语气像警察问话  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I sound like a cop, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.76,0:24:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.30,0:24:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,习惯成自然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, that's a force of habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.00,0:24:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  迈克  对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jeez, Mike, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.90,0:24:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不是故意要打听  -没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't mean to pry. - It's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.89,0:24:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃的来了  先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here you go, gents.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.92,0:24:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.40,0:24:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.76,0:24:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你饿着肚子离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you leave here hungry,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.90,0:24:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你自己的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's your own dang fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.26,0:24:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.41,0:24:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心  这些会上瘾的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Careful. They're addictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.63,0:24:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也许知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You might know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.58,0:25:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有比欧克莱尔更近的租车地方吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there anywhere closer than Eau Claire to rent a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.06,0:25:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}「湖畔镇日报」\N新酒店开张
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.81,0:25:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}「湖畔镇日报」\N暴风雨后码头需要修葺
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.95,0:25:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.37,0:25:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看谁和我一起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look who I got with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.00,0:25:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柴德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi, Chad.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.84,0:25:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安塞尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Ainsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.59,0:25:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房管小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ms. Property Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.11,0:25:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说你们俩见过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you two have met.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.57,0:25:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在枪口下认识的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At gun point.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.05,0:25:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安塞尔先生昨晚想闯进他的公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Ainsel tried to break into his apartment last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.13,0:25:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为钥匙不好使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Due to a key malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.98,0:25:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好没人受伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fortunately, no one was hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.58,0:25:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更明智的做法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the wiser course of action
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.03,0:25:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是打电话给当地的执法部门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}would have been to call your local law enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.56,0:25:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}「湖畔镇日报」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.87,0:25:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克想找交通工具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mike here is looking for some transportation,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.91,0:25:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到了桑迪的旧车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and, Sandy's old beater came to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.20,0:25:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那辆车不卖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The car is not for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.26,0:25:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车子已经停在后面差不多两年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's... been parked out back better part of two years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.01,0:26:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜在紧急情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Possible 10-99.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.44,0:26:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从马里埃尔·拉森的福特福莱克斯车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bag of laundry taken out
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.51,0:26:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了的洗衣店袋子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of Mariel Larson's Ford Flex.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.65,0:26:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强盗又来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bandit strikes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.80,0:26:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻赶过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}10-76.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.99,0:26:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}「湖畔镇日报」
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.10,0:26:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先声明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the record,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.29,0:26:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想租车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was only lookin' to rent the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.13,0:26:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想去芝加哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just trying to get to Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.66,0:26:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要去芝加哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's in Chicago?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.35,0:26:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参加朋友的追悼会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Memorial service for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.42,0:26:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天下午就走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I leave this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.17,0:26:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你要等个一两天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You may want to wait a day or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.48,0:26:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴风雨过后州际公路总是一片混乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The interstate's always a mess after a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.94,0:26:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我得去那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to be there tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.74,0:26:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但明天我就回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'll be back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.16,0:26:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两天一百美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A hundred dollars for the two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.33,0:26:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把车完好无损地开回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring it back like you found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.41,0:26:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我把车洗了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I get it cleaned up?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.97,0:26:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一百五十美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A hundred and fifty.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.20,0:26:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是唯一一把钥匙  别弄断了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the only key. Try not to break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.43,0:26:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.17,0:27:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真主至上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Allahu akbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.31,0:27:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会来开罗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What brings you back to Cairo?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.02,0:27:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我的新任务对星期三先生来说至关重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"My new mission is of vital importance to Mr. Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.48,0:27:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道需要多长时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know how long it will take
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.13,0:27:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是我会离开多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or how long I will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.63,0:28:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当这是我们旅程的终点吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Consider this the end of our journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.25,0:28:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别找我"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't look for me."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.70,0:28:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你对这个"任务"一无所知吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you know nothing of this "Mission"?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.32,0:28:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经好几月没见到星期三先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I haven't seen or heard anything
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.73,0:28:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有他的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from Mr. Wednesday in months.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.74,0:28:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I know is whatever task
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.45,0:28:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期三给精灵指派的任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wednesday has demanded of the Jinn,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.19,0:28:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们从此分离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it has driven us apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.20,0:28:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也许是精灵自己决定的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But perhaps the Jinn made up his own mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.70,0:28:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉会变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Feelings can change.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.70,0:28:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他真的不爱我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he truly does not love me,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.57,0:28:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要听他当面告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to hear him say it to my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.22,0:28:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去芝加哥参加科里亚达节\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm due in Chicago for the festival of Koliada.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.38,0:28:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旧神们聚集在一起悼念\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Old Gods are assembling to honor the ascendance
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.96,0:28:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卓娅·维切恩亚亚灵魂的归升\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of Zorya Vechernyaya's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.65,0:28:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精灵也会参加吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the Jinn will be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.78,0:28:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这个可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, it's... possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.68,0:29:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甘愿下七层地狱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would endure the seven gates of hell
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.30,0:29:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了解他内心的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to know the truth in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.80,0:29:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}临时混带  S·奥尔森
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.81,0:29:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,♪我知道  你不会回来♪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ I... know you won't come back ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.66,0:29:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,♪我也知道可能是我的错♪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ And I... know that it might be my fault ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.07,0:29:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,♪我有很多事想...♪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ And I've... got a lot to... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.58,0:29:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去趟超市  桑迪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm off to the store, Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.44,0:29:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈  我录音呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom. I'm recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.36,0:30:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  别忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, sorry. Listen, don't forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.30,0:30:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你答应过练习之后去接里昂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you promised to pick up Leon after practice. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.99,0:30:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱和你在一起的每一个时刻  卓娅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I loved every moment together with you, Zorya.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.52,0:30:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我讨厌你做的饭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I hated the food you cooked...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.21,0:30:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打心底讨厌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...with my entire soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.64,0:30:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.35,0:30:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一顿都在不断变差\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every meal worse than the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.03,0:31:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你回家一路顺风\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish you a safe journey home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.95,0:31:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朋友们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.85,0:31:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬我们最爱的卓娅·维切恩亚亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To our beloved Zorya Vechernyaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.76,0:31:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Skol!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.52,0:31:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.11,0:31:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  你怎么来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, what the hell are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.65,0:31:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去  没邀请你来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out. You were not invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.86,0:31:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没邀请我  可我还是来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neither was I! But here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.29,0:31:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.37,0:31:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有晚间之星的引导\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without our evening star to guide us,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.70,0:32:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的天空将永远阴暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the firmament is forever dimmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.77,0:32:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们两个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, the two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.78,0:32:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是应该在湖畔镇吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shouldn't you be in Lakeside?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.59,0:32:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是位非常特别的女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, she was a special lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.79,0:32:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是来找麻烦的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't come for any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.11,0:32:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礼物放在那边的桌子上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gifts go over there to table.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.66,0:32:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我带来了...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I brought, I brought...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.34,0:32:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就放那一堆上  礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. The same pile. Gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.96,0:32:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟给我  我想要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The cigarette, I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.51,0:32:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,节哀顺变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.03,0:32:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.28,0:32:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}米歇尔·斯马特  「旧情重燃在斐济」
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.40,0:32:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子进步了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The kid's learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.31,0:32:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你遗忘了最重要的部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, you missed the most important bit of all.
