Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.84,0:40:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扮演老男人的未婚妻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Playing the old man's fiancee?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.40,0:40:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That would be a no.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.76,0:40:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是女队的一员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm on the all-girls squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.75,0:40:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是怎么跟他在一起的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, how'd you end up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.61,0:40:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在克雷格列表网上发的贴子太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, his Craigslist post was dope,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.66,0:40:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我回复「有兴趣」\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I replied, "Interested".
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.00,0:40:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我只知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Next thing I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.00,0:40:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开着贝蒂  拿到现金报酬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm driving Betty and getting paid in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.99,0:40:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  你知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.21,0:40:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.39,0:40:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大三的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My junior year of Hunter,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.51,0:40:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被开除了  因为做黑客被捕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got kicked out, arrested for hacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.49,0:41:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我欠了一屁股债\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Up to my ass in debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.11,0:41:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When along comes the perfect job,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.75,0:41:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我最需要的时候来临了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}right when I needed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.72,0:41:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克雷格列表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Craigslist.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.95,0:41:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他帮我付清了律师费和学费\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He paid off my legal bills and tuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.28,0:41:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮他处理高科技的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I help him with... um, tech stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.36,0:41:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好消息是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the good news is,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.00,0:41:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我  你现在可以联系到你老爸了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on account of me, you can now reach your old man,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.87,0:41:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论何时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}day or night.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.20,0:41:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电话亭是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened to the phone booths?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.16,0:41:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  海拉程序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right? Hella progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.20,0:41:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  我和我老爸有很多麻烦事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I got all sorts of shit with my old man,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.63,0:41:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也许你可以考虑一下你爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but maybe consider your Pops
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.13,0:41:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不完全是个混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}isn't a complete fucking asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.02,0:41:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有点困难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, that is a stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.22,0:41:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.46,0:41:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你需要一个朋友聊聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if you ever need a friendly voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.63,0:41:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  不是他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I get it, not him,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.77,0:41:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打给那个号码吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just call the number.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.53,0:41:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你起码会接通我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll get me, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.89,0:42:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  听着  当事情变得难以处理时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, listen. When it all gets too much to handle,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.14,0:42:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总会这样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.28,0:42:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.89,0:42:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边发生什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell is going on in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.44,0:42:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期三\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.84,0:42:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}湖畔镇
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.13,0:42:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  梅宝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Mabel.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.35,0:42:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.46,0:43:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我再点馅饼的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I have another one of those pasties,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.12,0:43:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕吃四个都不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna want four more.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.03,0:43:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我还是悠着点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I am gonna take it easy
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.65,0:43:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我就点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I will have, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.19,0:43:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,培根配小麦土司吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}bacon and wheat toast, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.01,0:43:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.32,0:43:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柴德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.69,0:43:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}湖畔镇警局
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.58,0:44:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.28,0:44:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得问你几个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna have to ask you some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.26,0:44:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你下午四点出发去芝加哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You left for Chicago about 4 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.15,0:44:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开镇子之前停车加油了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You stop for gas before you left town?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.38,0:44:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.51,0:44:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.92,0:44:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在小镇大街的西铁古加油站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The, uh, the CITGO at, uh, Main.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.72,0:44:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.47,0:44:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉森·麦戈文昨天没去上学\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alison McGovern didn't show up to school
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.29,0:44:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没去上班\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or work yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.63,0:44:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她前天在亨宁斯店里下班之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one's seen or heard from her
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.85,0:44:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再就没人见过她  也没有过她的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}since her shift ended at Hennings the previous day.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.04,0:44:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克  要知道  这不是针对你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gotta understand, Mike, this is nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.46,0:45:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要梳理一下你过去72小时的行踪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're going to go over your whereabouts for the past 72.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.71,0:45:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且迈克  我需要你说得越详细越好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Mike, I need you be as specific as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.22,0:45:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题  去芝加哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure. It took about
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.02,0:45:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用了差不多七个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}seven hours to get to Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.51,0:45:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是去参加追悼会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were there for a memorial service.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.65,0:45:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是家人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This a family member?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.87,0:45:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叔叔的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Friend of my uncle's.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.28,0:45:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我住在...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I stayed at the, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.78,0:45:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东俄亥俄州的手绘酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Freehand Hotel, East Ohio.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.02,0:45:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后今天早晨开回来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And drove back this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.87,0:45:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挡风玻璃怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The windshield?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.09,0:45:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在36号公路撞了一只鹿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hit a deer on Route 36.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.40,0:45:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在斯蒂文斯波恩特的一家维修厂修了玻璃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The mechanic shop in Stevens Point fixed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.22,0:45:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  迈克  我需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, Mike. I am gonna need you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.96,0:45:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你准确的行车路线写下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to write down the exact route that you took
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.82,0:45:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要核查高速监控录像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so we can confirm that with highway surveillance cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.23,0:45:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Also gonna
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.82,0:45:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扣留车辆做一下鲁米诺试验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}need to hang on to the vehicle for a Luminol test.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.80,0:46:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.01,0:46:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能用个鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.06,0:47:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克  等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Mike. Wait, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.11,0:47:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是给不允许你用的壁炉烧的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that for the fireplace you're not allowed to use?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.51,0:47:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吧  干脆崩了我算了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what? Just shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.17,0:47:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行吗  这次来真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay? For real this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.37,0:47:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这样比冻死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because it's a lot quicker way to go
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.55,0:47:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛快得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than just freezing to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.89,0:47:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们两个一开始就有些误会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think maybe you and I got off on the wrong foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.11,0:47:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟柴德聊过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I spoke to Chad.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.72,0:48:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说你的事都核实无误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said your story checks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.75,0:48:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芝加哥  挡风玻璃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chicago, the windshield.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.19,0:48:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.80,0:48:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有艾莉森的消息吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything on Alison?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.06,0:48:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她的几个朋友谈了谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Talked to some of her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.24,0:48:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也不知道她有什么要离开镇子的缘由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one knows any reason why she might have left town
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.68,0:48:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道她可能去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or where she could've gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.66,0:48:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她家人正四处张贴传单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The family's putting up fliers
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.96,0:48:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请求志愿者帮助搜寻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and asking for volunteers to help in a search.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.34,0:48:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要帮忙就叫我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me know if I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.15,0:48:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, Mike...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.36,0:48:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用猎枪招呼你的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The thing with the shotgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.03,0:48:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That wasn't cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.72,0:48:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  是不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. It wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.73,0:49:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前把暖气的开关关上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had the breaker for the furnace turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.32,0:49:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这没人住  干嘛给空房间供暖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one was living here. Why heat an empty place?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.65,0:49:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点忘了给你这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, uh, almost forgot to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.25,0:49:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没让修车厂的人扔掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got the guys at the body shop to save it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.37,0:49:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计你儿子回来的时候可能想要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Figured your son might want it when he got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.87,0:49:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪上学  你没说过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's he at school? You didn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.91,0:49:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佛罗里达州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.92,0:49:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错  学什么专业的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice. What's he studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.12,0:49:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果暖气不热了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, if your heat goes out,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.44,0:49:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者你想封窗户  需要帮忙的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or you want some help insulating those windows,
